    "These findings provide important insights into how CTs propagate online conceptually and practically.",
    "Data collection for CT detectionSeveral studies have assembled datasets used to analyze CT content across various online sources.",
    "Common collection methods involve searching corpora using hashtags, key-words, or accounts associated with specific known CTs.",
    "Gerts et al. [13] used text collected from Twitter to categorize four COVID-19 CTs using random forest classification, providing context for each.",
